essig lastet. Han skal s\u00f8rge for at kj\u00f8ret\u00f8yet ogs\u00e5 under bruken er i forsvarlig stand og forsvarlig lastet.", "Eier av kj\u00f8ret\u00f8y eller den som p\u00e5 eierens vegne har r\u00e5dighet over det, plikter \u00e5 s\u00f8rge for at kj\u00f8ret\u00f8yet ikke brukes dersom det ikke er i forsvarlig stand.", "MER \u00c5 LESE: Sn\u00f8 og slaps stopper vogntog", "MER \u00c5 LESE: Sju timers bilberging p\u00e5 riksvei 70"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "590ffae5a5ca3dd8e9884bec4dd6e87f435e6a4339bcbac048d21b631f921676"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-11-06T20:00:25.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Statens vegvesen kj\u00f8rte \u00abdekkpatrulje\u00bb i Trondheim da sn\u00f8en kom."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article6591713.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Dekke%20f%C3%B8rste.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/ca39790d858f81ae5aa2d1f5953cabaa1ddd3be5.jpg?5981f0d6"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Flere b\u00f8telagt for kj\u00f8ring p\u00e5 sommerdekk -adressa.no", "Tatt med sommerdekk", "Totalvurdering", "Spent p\u00e5 mildv\u00e6ret"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "ca39790d858f81ae5aa2d1f5953cabaa1ddd3be5"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "automotive"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["forsvarlig stand", "kj\u00f8ret\u00f8y", "kj\u00f8re videre", "sommerdekk", "d\u00e5rlig skodd", "kj\u00f8re", "dekk"]}, {"field": "kw-entit